data.description: Looking for a small cabin or tiny home with all sports lake access? This remodeled and update home could be what your looking for. Sitting on a double lot with boat docking on Chippewa Lake at end of the street!  This home has been gutted over the past several years from top to bottom and everything is new!  The large yard has plenty of room to build a garage or pole barn for all of your storage needs. Call today and come check out this great home as summer will be here before you know it!
